<h2 style="color: #1e3a8a; text-align: center;">📚 About Us</h2>
<p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555; text-align: center;">
    Welcome to <strong>Nai Subha Kids Paradise School</strong>, where young minds embark on a journey of learning, creativity, and growth! 
